Package org.fcrepo.camel.reindexing

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PathProcessor
    A processor that converts the body of a message (which should be a full fedora resource URI) into the corresponding CamelFcrepoIdentifier value.
    ReindexingHeaders
    A class defining header values for the indexing routes
    ReindexingRouter
    A content router for handling JMS events.
    RestProcessor
    A processor that converts the REST uri into the identifying path for an fcrepo node.
    UsageProcessor
    A processor to generate some useful documentation on the usage of this service.
